---
---
<section class="workflow" aria-labelledby="h-flow">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2 id="h-flow">A default path through the work</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">
      Not a product requirement — a <strong>convention</strong> the README encodes. Skip steps when
      the task is small.
    </p>
    <div class="flow" aria-label="Default workflow order">
      <div class="flow-row">
        <span class="flow-step">user prompt</span>
        <span class="flow-arrow">→</span>
        <span class="flow-step">brainstorm</span>
        <span class="flow-arrow">→</span>
        <span class="flow-step">planning_brief</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-row" style="margin-top:0.5rem">
        <span class="flow-arrow" style="opacity:0.6">↓</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-row">
        <span class="flow-step">implementer</span>
        <span class="flow-arrow">→</span>
        <span class="flow-step">tester</span>
        <span class="flow-arrow">→</span>
        <span class="flow-step">reviewer</span>
        <span class="flow-arrow">→</span>
        <span class="flow-step">ship_writer</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="flow-note">
      Decks and docs can also branch from the initial prompt (e.g. <strong>presentation-creation</strong>).
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
